# Enterprise Web Stack Integration Guide

## Overview

This guide covers integration of the Enterprise Web Stack pattern (CORE-21)
into a new SW-WEB-* project. The stack provides:

- **Auth**: NextAuth + optional SSO (LDAP/SAML/OIDC)
- **RBAC**: Role/permission schema + policy middleware
- **Audit**: Hash-chained audit log for every write operation
- **Reports**: Tabular + chart components (Tremor / shadcn)
- **i18n**: next-intl with {{ supported_locales | length }} locale bundles
- **Multi-tenant**: tenant_id column + row-level security
- **Import/Export**: CSV/XLSX/JSON round-trip
- **Workflow**: State machine + approval chain

