## API Reference

Base path: `/api/enterprise/`

### Auth
- `GET /auth/providers` — List configured auth providers
- `POST /auth/authenticate` — Authenticate with a provider
- `POST /auth/session` — Create a new session
- `POST /auth/session/validate` — Validate session token

### RBAC
- `GET /rbac/roles` — List all roles
- `GET /rbac/permissions` — List all permissions
- `POST /rbac/enforce` — Check policy enforcement

### Audit
- `POST /audit/write` — Write an audit entry
- `POST /audit/query` — Query audit log
- `POST /audit/verify` — Verify hash chain integrity

### Reports
- `GET /reports/types` — List report types
- `POST /reports/generate` — Generate a report
- `POST /reports/export` — Export a report

### Tenants
- `POST /tenants` — Create a tenant
- `GET /tenants` — List tenants
- `POST /tenants/rls` — Apply RLS to a query

### Import/Export
- `POST /import/preview` — Preview import data
- `POST /import/execute` — Execute import
- `POST /export/execute` — Execute export

### Workflow
- `POST /workflow/instances` — Create workflow instance
- `POST /workflow/instances/{id}/transition` — Transition state
- `POST /workflow/instances/{id}/approve` — Approve
- `POST /workflow/instances/{id}/reject` — Reject

## Testing

Run all enterprise web stack tests:

```bash
python -m pytest backend/tests/test_enterprise_web_stack.py -v
```

Run specific test recipes:

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:8000/api/enterprise/test-recipes/full_integration/run
```
